Package: RSwissPos
Title: Easy access to data on Swiss Direct Democracy and methods to measure parties' and the public's ideological positions.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Maxime", "Walder", , "maxime.walder", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Enables users to get easy access to data on Swiss direct democracy. 
    In addition, it provides posterior estimates of ballot discrimination that allow researchers to 
    compute the position of political parties and municipalities similarly as Walder (2025). 
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
